column2: SELECT d.dr7ObjID,s.plate,s.fiberid,s.mjd,s.ra,s.dec,s.z,gs.D4#_N_SUB,gs.D4#_N_SUB_ERR,gs.LICK_HD_A_SUB,gs.LICK_HD_A_SUB_ERR,gl.H_ALPHA_FLUX,gl.H_ALPHA_FLUX_ERR,gl.H_BETA_FLUX,    gl.H_BETA_FLUX_ERR,gl.OIII_#_FLUX,gl.OIII_#_FLUX_ERR,gl.NII_#_FLUX,gl.OI_#_FLUX,gl.OI_#_FLUX_ERR,gl.NII_#_FLUX_ERR,   ge.lgm_tot_p5#,ge.sfr_tot_p5#,ge.lgm_fib_p5#,ge.sfr_fib_p5#,gi.sn_median,gl.sigma_balmer,gl.sigma_balmer_err,gl.H_ALPHA_EQW,gl.H_ALPHA_EQW_ERR,gl.OII_#_FLUX,gl.OII_#_FLUX_ERR,   gl.OII_#_FLUX,gl.OII_#_FLUX_ERR,gl.SII_#_FLUX,gl.SII_#_FLUX_ERR,gl.SII_#_FLUX,gl.SII_#_FLUX_ERR,   gi.v_disp,gi.v_disp_err,ge.bptclass,ph.petroR5#_r,ph.petroR9#_r,ph.petroR5#_i,ph.petroR9#_i,ph.petroR5#_z,ph.petroR9#_z,ph.modelMag_g,ph.modelMag_z,ph.modelMagErr_g,ph.modelMagErr_z,   ph.extinction_g,ph.extinction_z,gl.sigma_forbidden,gl.sigma_forbidden_err from SpecObj as s into mydb.sdss_dr7_jhu_sample    JOIN photoobjall as ph on s.bestObjID=ph.objID JOIN galSpecIndx as gs on s.specObjID=gs.specObjID JOIN galSpecInfo as gi on s.specObjID=gi.specObjID JOIN galSpecLine as gl on s.specObjID=gl.specObjID JOIN galSpecExtra as ge on s.specObjID=ge.specObjID   INNER JOIN specDR7 as d on d.specObjID =s.specObjID      WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND #
